comments_full:
[{'comment_id': '1534189837392877', 'comment_url': 'https://facebook.com/1534189837392877', 'commenter_id': '1465283393', 'commenter_url': 'https://facebook.com/linsay.patterson?eav=AfbSQvrLvhhf62o6S_Sf-vo5G8Dl5u39WbfOMv1mP_fZ3IOy9gvyiooLFhn2lcJlgIU&fref=nf&rc=p&refid=52&__tn__=R&paipv=0', 'commenter_name': 'Linsay Patterson', 'commenter_meta': 'Top fan', 'comment_text': 'RPH Australia Pty Ltd was trading under the name GJ Gardner Perth West as it was part of the GJ Gardner network, a major building franchisor which has nearly 100 independent building companies and offices dotted around Australia.
